Introduction

Byun Eui Joo, known under his stage name EJ, is a South Korean singer and dancer under HYBE Labels Japan. He is best known as the leader, one of the rappers and vocalists of the Japanese boy group &Team.

EJ participated on the survival program I-LAND–the same show were ENHYPEN was created. However, EJ got eliminated in episode 7. In 2022, he participated in the survival show "&AUDITION - The Howling -" where he qualified to become a member of the Japanese boy group &TEAM.
